                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="slide-item absolute bottom-[18%] right-[22%]">
                <div class="text-sm text-red-300/70 italic flex items-center gap-2">
                  <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-400/60"></div>
                  Geen vaste grond om op te landen
